This Week's Podcast- TB284 
The #COVID19 pandemic ends with widespread vaccine compliance, but a formidable misinformation campaign seeks to derail public health efforts. I speak with Dr. Rahul Gupta from March of Dimes about #vaccine hesitancy. @DrGuptaMD https://t.co/EFNfZoZpjq https://t.co/s2rjjM9G7z
